title: Inherit a title
beginning: Take 10 rank 1 schemes from the bank into your hand
end: Take 5 gold

title: Sacrifice a Pawn
beginning: Draw 2
end: Trash 1 from your hand

title: Fight for freedom
beginning: Draw a number of schemes equal to the lowest time in play
end: Draw 1 for each dungeon scheme

title: Serve as Sheriff
beginning: Draw 1
end: Summon a rank 1 scheme from the bank to the court

title: Declare independence
beginning: Take a rank 1 scheme from the bank into your hand
end: Draw a number of schemes equal to the lowest time in play

title: Frame the hostage
beginning: Draw a number of schemes equal to the highest time in play
end: Draw a number of schemes equal to the lowest rank in the dungeon

title: Found a secret order
beginning: Draw your last reserve
end: Draw twice the number of colors in play

title: Host a wedding
beginning: If the left 2 timeline schemes are the same color, earn the higher rank in coin
end: Earn the highest time in play in silver

title: Buccaneer a treasure ship
beginning: Copy the lowest rank yellow scheme in play
end: Copy the lowest rank green or yellow dungeon scheme
bonus: If this is the highest rank scheme in play, reserve it instead of summoning or imprisoning it

title: Start a bloodfeud
beginning: If your last reserve is yellow, copy it
end: Copy the highest rank green scheme in play
bonus: If you have this in play at the end of an auction you lose, the winner must imprison their last reserve

title: Call in allies
beginning: Copy the leftmost yellow timeline scheme
end: Copy highest rank yellow scheme in play
bonus: If you have this in play during the auction, your bid is increased by 10

title: Challenge to a duel
beginning: If your last reserve is green or yellow, copy it
end: Copy the lowest rank green or yellow scheme in play
bonus: If you have this in play during the auction, you may bid silver

title: Storm the palace
beginning: If the leftmost timeline scheme is green or yellow, copy it
end: Copy the highest rank green dungeon scheme
bonus: If you have this in play after you won the auction, including buying it, you may take cards from the dungeon as well as the court

title: Spread the rebellion
beginning: If there are no red timeline schemes, copy the leftmost timeline scheme
end: Copy the highest rank green or yellow scheme in play
bonus: If you have this in play at end of an auction you lose, the winner may not take schemes from the court

title: Plunder the enemy
beginning: If there is a lower rank scheme in play, copy the rightmost yellow timeline scheme
end: Copy the highest rank green or yellow dungeon scheme
bonus: If only you have this in play at the end of an auction, including buying it, you may reorder your reserve after reserving this

title: Defeat the church
beginning: If your last reserve is red, copy the leftmost green timeline scheme
end: Otherwise, copy your last reserve
bonus: If you summon this to the court, copy it

title: Evict the tenants
beginning: Earn 25 gold
end: Trash 1 from your hand

title: Blackmail her Majesty
beginning: Earn the leftmost timeline scheme's rank in coin
end: If the highest scheme in play is yellow, earn its rank in coin

title: Smuggle contraband
beginning: If your last reserve is yellow, earn twice its rank in coin
end: If you took gold, move your last reserve to the start of your reserve

title: Choose the next Pope
beginning: Pay your last reserve's rank
end: Earn 30 gold

title: Learn ancient alchemy
beginning: Earn twice your last reserve's rank in coin
end: If it is not yellow, summon it to the court

title: Marry the Duchess
beginning: Pay five times the left timeline scheme's time
end: Earn twice its rank in coin

title: Collect alms
beginning: Earn 5 gold for each dungeon scheme
end: Earn the rightmost timeline scheme's rank in coin

title: Enclose peasant land
beginning: Earn the lowest green rank in play in coin
end: Draw a number of schemes equal to your last reserve's time

title: Rule alongside your mother
beginning: If your last reserve is green, draw 5
end: If the highest or lowest rank scheme in play is green, draw 5

title: Become a Saint
beginning: If you have 50 or less gold, draw 5
end: If your reserve has 5 or less schemes, draw 5
